#  ▐█▀▀█▄▐█ ▌▐▌▐█·▐█·██ ▪ ██ ▄▄▄▀▀▀█▄   ║║║ ║ ║ ╠╣ ║║  ║╣ ╚═╗
#  ██▄▪▐███ ██▌▐█▌▐█▌▐█▌ ▄▐███▌▐█▄▪▐█  ═╩╝╚═╝ ╩ ╚  ╩╩═╝╚═╝╚═╝
#  ·▀▀▀▀ ▀▀  █▪▀▀▀▀▀▀.▀▀▀ ·▀▀▀  ▀▀▀▀   https://dot.bmilcs.com
#                 APT INSTALLER [./yi]

source _bm
_t apt install 


#sudo apt list\
#  | fzf -m \
#  --preview 'sudo apt-cache show {1}' \
#  | sudo apt install -y -

sudo apt-cache search '' \
  | sort \
  | cut --delimiter ' ' --fields 1 \
  | fzf --multi --cycle --reverse --preview 'apt-cache show {1}' \
  | xargs -r sudo apt install -y
